.box.static-container
  %h4.first Go Pro
  
  %p You can support drop.sc by getting an ads free pro account.
  Benefits:
  %ul
    %li No ads
    %li Access to premium features when released
  
  %p
    The price is $2. Pro status is valid for 3 months after activation.
  
  Instructions:
  - if user_signed_in?
    %p 
      Click Pay now below and follow the Paypal instructions.
    
      <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post">
      <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
      <table>
      <tr><td><input type="hidden" name="on0" value="user_id">User ID</td></tr><tr><td><input type="text" name="os0" maxlength="60"></td></tr>
      </table>
      <input type="hidden" name="encrypted" value="-----BEGIN PKCS7----------END PKCS7-----
      ">
      <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_paynowCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">
      <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">
      </form>

      <script type="application/javascript">
      != "$('input[name=cmd]').parent().find('table').hide();"
      != "$('input[name=os0]').val('#{current_user.id}');"
      </script>
    %p Note: The pro account is us  ually activated within 24 hours. The account you are currently logged in will be promoted.

    %p Thank you for your support.
  - else
    != "Please #{link_to "sign up", new_user_registration_path} or #{link_to('login', new_user_session_path(:return_url => request.path))} to upgrade to pro."